attribute.value: A component instantiation has only a single location
A Receptacle could only be connected to the Facet of the same interface type.
All event_ports could only be connected to the port of the same event_type.

regnode.name: Annotation about event_type
regnode.value:
An Event_Type can have multiple fields in it.
The lowest level of the field type will be C++/CORBA types.
I wonder if we need to model on this level..but for now I just keep it here to remind myself.

involved in the interpretor. I use the name of the
interface to to constraint checking.
